  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Norepinephrine (NE) infusion is used prophylactically to counteract the vasodilator effect of
      spinal anesthesia. prophylactic use of NE infusion is expected to decrease bouts of
      hypotension, vomiting and increase patient satisfaction
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
